response.original_title: フェイスペインティングガール
response.overview: Akibacom's production department presents a face-painting messy work! Miyoko-chan came to the shoot without knowing anything. She never expected to be made up like a clown! She continues to be embarrassed from start to finish. What's more, she goes for a walk outside in that outfit, which is an embarrassing play! After that, her face is painted black and she gets naughty! This is a work full of girls' embarrassment!
response.title: Face Painting Girl
